      "content": "\"Being patient\" just feels like more suffering. It's like you're telling me to just sit here and let the sadness crush me. I don't want to \"navigate\" this anymore. I just want the peace of not having to feel any of this. Is that even a thing? To just... not have to deal with it all?",
